      "text": "実は、ララ達が来てからというもの\n寮の風紀が乱れに乱れているんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.4222736044,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_01-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "ララの発明品の誤作動でトラブルが起きたり……\nこの間なんか、みんなが動物になっちゃったんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.2889431002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "彼女の発明品は本当になんでもありだな……\nだから身体検査を受けさせられたのか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.9875125029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_01-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "そうなんです。もしかしてララの発明品を\n持ってるんじゃないかと思ったので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.2723418556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_01-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "本当に困っているんです\nこころが積極的にいたずらに使いますし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.005675189,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
