      "text": "はい、本当に困ったものです\n……って、何想像してるんですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.7193087677,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_01/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_15_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "べ、別に変なことは考えていないぞ！？\nそもそも怜が言ったんじゃないか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 222.6999704997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
